246
00:19:20,760 --> 00:19:22,072
Kau merasa takut?

247
00:19:25,290 --> 00:19:26,400
Sampai jumpa.

248
00:19:37,240 --> 00:19:39,739
Apakah aktris C kehilangan akal?

249
