302
00:22:14,760 --> 00:22:16,477
Kami semua patungan 10.000 won.

303
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:18,381
Minta dia untuk membayarmu.

304
00:22:19,670 --> 00:22:21,215
Hei, Jeong Joo Hwan.

305
00:22:24,639 --> 00:22:27,741
